title: 11/04/21 DPS Hour 3 Mary Kay Cabot
itunes:title: 11/04/21 DPS Hour 3 Mary Kay Cabot
description:
Browns beat writer for Cleveland.com and The Plain Dealer Mary Kay Cabot joins The Dan Patrick Show to talk about the ongoing drama with the Browns, Baker Mayfield, and Odell Beckham Jr, where it appears that Odell's camp has decided it's time to move the WR out of Cleveland.
